; Balance Assertions Beancount File
; Testing balance directives

2014-01-01 open Assets:US:BofA:Checking USD
2014-01-01 open Assets:US:BofA:Savings USD
2014-01-01 open Income:US:Salary

; Initial deposit
2014-01-05 * "Initial deposit"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  1000.00 USD
  Income:US:Salary  -1000.00 USD

; Balance assertion - checking account should have 1000 USD
2014-01-05 balance Assets:US:BofA:Checking  1000.00 USD

; Another transaction
2014-01-10 * "Deposit"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  500.00 USD
  Income:US:Salary  -500.00 USD

; Balance assertion - should now have 1500 USD
2014-01-10 balance Assets:US:BofA:Checking  1500.00 USD

; Transfer to savings
2014-01-15 * "Transfer"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  -300.00 USD
  Assets:US:BofA:Savings  300.00 USD

; Balance assertion - checking should have 1200
2014-01-15 balance Assets:US:BofA:Checking  1200.00 USD

; Balance assertion - savings should have 300
2014-01-15 balance Assets:US:BofA:Savings  300.00 USD

; Multiple currencies in balance
2014-02-01 open Assets:Multiple:Currencies USD, EUR, CAD

2014-02-01 balance Assets:Multiple:Currencies 1000 USD, 500 EUR, 200 CAD